Release Notes for Version 3.14.0
================================

Overview
--------

Release 3.14.0 is the 1st release in
the Errata Tool 3.14 development period. It closes [22 bugs and RFEs][buglist].

This release of Errata Tool includes fixes for JIRA issue and bug syncing, a
fix for an error raised in some cases when checking signatures, plus a number
of other bug fixes and usability improvements.

